關措施，例如限制餐廳只可外賣，關閉非必要的企業，讓大多數人留在家中，或是推行更嚴厲的邊境管制等。</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%99%B3%E6%99%BA%E6%80%9D-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4-%E5%8A%A0%E8%BE%A3-%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9F-%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E9%9D%9E%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2580%259D-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%25BE%25A3-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%25A3%259F-%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25BF%2585%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%2F&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=e2674976\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2580%259D-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%25BE%25A3-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%25A3%259F-%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%2596%2589%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25BF%2585%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%2F&h=536061ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%99%B3%E6%99%BA%E6%80%9D-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4-%E5%8A%A0%E8%BE%A3-%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9F-%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E9%9D%9E%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:48:00.000Z","msg":"條link虧虧地，貼多次source <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%99%B3%E6%99%BA%E6%80%9D-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4-%E5%8A%A0%E8%BE%A3-%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9F-%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E9%9D%9E%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.